data.description:
Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located on Jacksonville's Westside.
 Step inside to discover recently updated bathrooms and a kitchen adorned with beautiful granite countertops, giving the space a fresh and stylish feel. 
The open-concept layout allows for seamless flow between the living areas, perfect for both entertaining and daily living. 
One standout feature of this home is the Florida room, providing a light-filled space that can be used as a versatile bonus area, such as a home office, playroom, or relaxation space. With tile and laminate wood flooring throughout, this home strikes the ideal balance between style and practicality.Seller will provide a stove and refrigerator prior to closing. Safety is a top priority here, as evidenced by the inclusion of a safety gate with remote access, ensuring peace of mind for you and your loved ones. Additionally, the large fenced-in yard offers plenty of space for outdoor activities and gatherings. For added convenience, there is a detached shed, providing ample storage space for all your tools and equipment. Located in Jacksonvilles' Westside, this home offers easy access to nearby amenities, schools, shopping centers, and parks, making it an ideal choice for families and individuals alike. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful house your new home.
